Here is a clean, production-ready implementation of **Debounce function utility (variant 25)** in Javascript.

### Explanation
Delays executing the passed function until after 'wait' milliseconds have elapsed since the last call. Specifically, this handles variant case 25.

### Implementation
```javascript
function debounce_v25(func, wait) {
  let timeout;
  return function(...args) {
    clearTimeout(timeout);
    timeout = setTimeout(() => func.apply(this, args), wait);
  };
}
```

