Delays executing the passed function until after 'wait' milliseconds have elapsed since the last call. Specifically, this handles variant case 19.

### Implementation
```javascript
function debounce_v19(func, wait) {
  let timeout;
  return function(...args) {
    clearTimeout(timeout);
    timeout = setTimeout(() => func.apply(this, args), wait);
  };
}
```

